    <abilityid>melee.shield_push</abilityid>
    <abilityclass>Slow</abilityclass>
    <abilitydescription>
      <p>
	<indexentry>shield push</indexentry>
	The character can use the shield to push an adjacent opponent
	back in a direction chosen by the character.  The opponent must
	be corporeal, capable of being moved, and not too much larger
	than the character.
      </p>
    </abilitydescription>
